        <h3>2. Your Missions</h3>
        <p>Follow the instructions in the "Messages" app on the phone. Here is a summary of what to look for:
        </p>

        <ul class="custom-list">
            <li><strong>Browser:</strong> Look at the Cookie Banner. What is the difference between "Necessary"
                and "All" cookies?</li>
            <li><strong>Connectify:</strong> Read the permissions carefully. Does a social app really need your
                location <em>all the time</em>? Check the Terms & Conditions for the "Data Retention" rule.</li>
            <li><strong>MapMe:</strong> Compare "While Using App" vs "Always Allow". Why would an app want to
                track you when you aren't using it?</li>
            <li><strong>SkyWatch:</strong> Try "Approximate Location". Do you still get the weather? What is the
                privacy benefit?</li>
        </ul>

        <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 1.5rem 0;">

