            <h4 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--primary-color);">B. The Trade-off</h4>
            <p>Give one example where you had to choose between <strong>Privacy</strong> (keeping data safe) and
                <strong>Convenience</strong> (making the app easier to use). What did you choose and why?
            </p>
